{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/BannerPromoNoLogo.png?t=1728896760\" />In Little Repair Shop you will receive requests from customers who will ask you to <strong>repair their beloved consoles</strong>.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After accepting the request, the order will arrive at your desk and the process can begin!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/ezgif-1-6417f386bc.gif?t=1728896760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What you repair also becomes<strong> part of your collection</strong> and can be <strong>customized </strong>with new <strong>colors</strong>, <strong>patterns </strong>and <strong>stickers</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/Repair.gif?t=1728896760\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features a <strong>cozy and relaxing experience</strong>: <strong>take care</strong> of consoles and make them <strong>unique </strong>to create the perfect collection.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247390/extras/Custom.gif?t=1728896760\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy a relaxing, wholesome experience surrounded by pastel colors and relaxing music!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Respond to customer requests and help them!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Restore old consoles to their former glory!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your consoles with many cute stickers and different color palettes!</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/